article.description: — Antonio Reeves had 30 points as Illinois State got past Chicago State 80-71 on Saturday.
article.headline: Reeves lifts Illinois State past Chicago State 80-71
article.linkText: Reeves lifts Illinois State past Chicago State 80-71
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Antonio Reeves had 30 points as Illinois State got past Chicago State 80-71 on Saturday. Reeves shot 6 for 8 from deep. Josiah Strong had 19 points for Illinois State (5-5). Howard Fleming Jr. added 10 points. Kendall Lewis had seven rebounds. Jahsean Corbett had 17 points and six rebounds for the Cougars (3-6). Coreyoun Rushin added 13 points and nine rebounds. Dominique Alexander and Favour Chukwukelu each had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
